net.objectzoo.events.impl

Interface Event2AsyncDelegate<T1,T2>

  • Type Parameters:
    T1 - The type of the first information parameter the event provides
    T2 - The type of the second information parameter the event provides
    All Superinterfaces:
    Action2<T1,T2>, Action2Async<T1,T2>, java.util.function.BiConsumer<T1,T2>, Event2<T1,T2>, Event2Delegate<T1,T2>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Event2AsyncAdapter

    public interface Event2AsyncDelegate<T1,T2>
extends Action2Async<T1,T2>, Event2Delegate<T1,T2>
    An Event2AsyncDelegate implements Action2Async as well as Event2Delegate and is meant as a specification for implementations that delegate calls to the Action2Async interface asynchronously to all subscribers of the Event2Delegate interface.
